---
title: "US49 — View service requests"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>RequestsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ViewServiceRequests
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ServiceRequest
  A->>B: open Requests tab
  B->>C: load(expertId)
  C->>E: listServiceRequests(expertId)
  alt requests found
    E-->>C: List of ServiceRequest (pending / accepted / completed)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (request list)
    B-->>A: who asked, for what, when
  else none yet
    E-->>C: empty list
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (empty)
    B-->>A: "No requests yet."
  end
  note over E: listServiceRequests via SupabaseGateway → service_requests (RLS — own services only)
